# SPECTRAL PCM — Slide Production System

## Toolchain
- **pptxgenjs** — Node.js PowerPoint build tool. All slides are generated programmatically.
- **Higgsfield** — AI image generation for all slide photography
- **LibreOffice / pdftoppm** — Visual QA: convert PPTX → PDF → JPEGs for inspection

## File Structure for Phase 7 Production
```
phase7/
├── _master/
│   ├── BUILD_CONSTANTS.js      ← brand tokens, shared layout helpers
│   ├── SLIDE_MASTER.pptx       ← reference template (do not edit programmatically)
│   └── img16x9.js              ← Higgsfield image helper function
├── d1/
│   ├── d1p1_build.js           ← build script for D1P1
│   ├── d1p1_higgsfield.md      ← Higgsfield prompt batch for D1P1
│   ├── d1p1_output.pptx        ← generated output
│   ├── img/                    ← Higgsfield renders for this pack
│   └── [repeat for d1p2–d1p5]
├── d2/
│   └── [d2p1–d2p6]
├── d3/
│   └── [d3p1–d3p6]
└── scn/
