## Build Script Skeleton
```js
// phase7/d1/d1p1_build.js
const pptx = new PptxGenJS()
const { BRAND, FONT, CLASSIF_TEXT, SLIDE } = require('../_master/BUILD_CONSTANTS')
const { img16x9 } = require('../_master/img16x9')

pptx.layout = 'LAYOUT_WIDE'  // 16:9

// Slide 1 — Cover
const s1 = pptx.addSlide()
buildCover(pptx, s1, {
  imgPath: './img/d1p1_cover.jpg',
  title: 'THE DRONE REVOLUTION',
  subtitle: 'Why This Matters Now — Day 1, Pack 1',
})

// Slide 2 — Learning Objectives
const s2 = pptx.addSlide()
buildLOs(pptx, s2, {
  lessonTitle: 'The Drone Revolution',
  los: [
    'Articulate why UAS dominance is the defining characteristic of 2020s warfare',
    'Classify five spine facts by operational domain',
    'Assess threat implications for their own operating environment',
  ],
  assessmentType: 'Knowledge check — 10 MCQ + class discussion',
})

// ... continue for remaining slides

pptx.writeFile({ fileName: './d1p1_output.pptx' })
  .then(() => console.log('D1P1 written'))
  .catch(console.error)
```

## Higgsfield Workflow

### Step 1 — Generate prompts file alongside the build script
File: `phase7/d1/d1p1_higgsfield.md`
```markdown
## D1P1 — The Drone Revolution

### Slide 1 (Cover) — The Drone Revolution
**Purpose:** Establish the operational weight of modern UAS — not toys, not gadgets, war-decisive systems
**Style:** cinematic military documentary, desaturated, warm golden hour grading, high contrast
**Subject:** Shahed-136 OWA drone in low-level flight over Eastern European farmland, sunset horizon,
           burning wreckage visible in background, second drone visible high right frame
**Mood:** tense, operationally credible, ominous
**Aspect:** 16:9
**Negative:** cartoon, low quality, watermark, civilian aesthetic, cheerful, text overlay

### Slide 5 (Full-bleed) — Ukraine 4 Million Drones
**Purpose:** Communicate the industrial scale of Ukraine's drone production
**Style:** cinematic documentary, desaturated, cool blue-grey factory lighting
**Subject:** Military drone production line, dozens of FPV frames being assembled by technicians in
           industrial facility, overhead lighting, blue/grey tones
**Mood:** industrial, determined, scaled
**Aspect:** 16:9
**Negative:** cartoon, low quality, watermark, cheerful, bright colours, text
```

